Description: The goal of tidytags is to sync together 
    (a) the ease of collecting tweets over time with a 
    **Twitter Archiving Google Sheet** [TAGS](https://tags.hawksey.info/), 
    (b) the utility of the **rtweet** [package](https://rtweet.info/) for 
    processing and preparing additional Twitter metadata, and 
    (c) a collection of different analytic functions developed during the course 
    of extensive social media research in education.
